  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK769">
<l>ciṟumaiyuñ cellāt tuṉiyum vaṟumaiyu</l>
<l>millāyiṉ vellum paṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>An army can triumph (over its foes) if it is free from diminution irremediable aversion and poverty.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
